  year            = {2013},
  address         = {Gaithersburg, MD, USA},
  month           = {19--23 Nov.},
  abstract        = {We describe the participation of the Lowlands at the Web Track and the FedWeb track of TREC 2013. For the Web Track we used the Mirex Map-Reduce library with out-of-thebox approaches and for the FedWeb Track we adapted our shard selection method Taily for resource selection. Here, our results were above median and close to the maximum performance achieved.},
